node.text: iv been working out for the last 6 months but today officially marks Day 1 for me because im on the road...i got working out from home down packed but now i have to incorporate it into my crazy lifestyle but I am determined.  Woke up and called my trainer @bodies.of.art.fitness for my workout and got to it... @jdee313 chk me out ‼️ This is not just to lose weight, it’s really a lifestyle...once i embraced that my life changed 🙏🏽 Proud of the work I put in the last 6 months and looking forward to the next 6 💪🏽
